These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: plum, avocado
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, spy
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person eating avocado is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Food   | avocado    | plum |
| Movie-Genre         | spy | action    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat
2 different games are played: whist, billiard
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person playing whist is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Pet      | goat  | chinchilla   |
| Game   | billiard | whist  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, domino
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, cain
1. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Game         | monopoly   | domino  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy  |
| Cigar         | game   | cain |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
City: hamburg, new-york
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, april
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| City          | hamburg | new-york |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | fantasy   |
| Birthday     | april       | august      |

