.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bongani
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, aconite
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
3. the oliveros-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Cigar    | bongani | oliveros     |
| Flower     | aconite | zinnia |
| Sport   | skiing | sailing    |

 #################################

 
