.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, romance
The people have 2 different jobs:  pilot, fisherman
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, magic-tricks
1. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
2. the fisherman is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | romance |
| Job   | pilot  | fisherman  |
| Hobby     | magic-tricks | hiking    |

 